# ShellCheck configuration for Leo's Profiles.
#
# SC2034 (variable appears unused): the installer is a step-based state machine
# that shares many globals across functions (OPT_*/ENV_* parsed in one function,
# read in resolve_plan/run_wizard/main; STATE_*/PKG_SKIP/RESUMING/WIZARD_RAN
# likewise). ShellCheck analyses assignments per-construct and reports these as
# unused even though every one is read elsewhere in the same file (verified).
# Disabling SC2034 repo-wide avoids a wall of false positives; genuinely dead
# code is caught in review instead.
disable=SC2034
